videos.description: Damian Lillard passes out Robert Covington who pulls up and knocks down a corner 3-pointer to beat the buzzer and give the Blazers a 73-72 lead.

videos.description: Chris Paul throws a sweet bounce pass to Deandre Ayton who goes up to smash down a powerful two-handed dunk in the lane.

videos.description: Chris Paul drives and pulls up to knock down a difficult midrange jumper over a defender to tie the game at 102-102 with only a few seconds remaining in the fourth quarter.
